This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with speech recognition and acoustic models. It could also belong to cs.SD (Sound) as it deals with audio data. The paper also involves machine learning techniques, which could place it in cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper discusses adaptation techniques, which could place it in cs.SD (Systems and Control).
